    <!-- Why Johns Island -->
    <section class="section light">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Why Johns Island Is a Prime Market for Direct Mail</h2>
                <p>Johns Island is one of the fastest-growing communities in the Charleston metro, with massive new development transforming this historic Sea Island into a magnet for young families and new homeowners.</p>
